OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy bill support for    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffirms to be cut from April 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government will scale back support 
OL,6, for businesses with energy bills after 
OL,7, warning that the current level of help 
OL,8, was too expensive.                     
OL,10,FUnder the new scheme, firms will get a 
OL,11,Fdiscount on wholesale prices rather    
OL,12,Fthan costs being capped as under the   
OL,13,Fcurrent one.                           
OL,15,FHeavy energy-using sectors, like glass,
OL,16,Fceramics and steelmakers, will get a   
OL,17,Flarger discount than others.           
OL,19,FBut firms will only benefit from the   
OL,20,Fscheme when energy bills are high.     
